# Funnel Architecture

- Funnel URLs are root-level (`/slug`) and must be resolved only via explicit registry in `src/funnels/registry.ts`.
- Do not add locale prefix (`/it`, `/en`) to funnel routes.
- Keep all non-funnel pages under the existing locale flow.
- Use middleware rewrite to internal route namespace (`/__funnels/...`) to avoid dynamic route conflicts.
- Never treat unregistered slugs as funnels.
